      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes a new Locator/ID Separation Protocol (LISP) Canonical Address Format (LCAF), the Vendor-Specific LCAF.  This LCAF enables organizations to have implementation-specific encodings for LCAF addresses.  This document updates RFC 8060.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
